title: I LOVE LISTS
description: Ready to plan some edible holiday gifts?  I have a small obsession with plastic photobox cases.  Nature photographer captures an all-black penguin. Let’s look at some wild hotel rooms.  Bad tattoos are bad!  International landscape photographer wanderlust! Some airport tips from TSA for holiday traveling.  Your old digital camera maybe worth a lot.  Tips for photographing a wedding.  What do dryer sheets actually do?  These major brands own all the food you eat.  I am always looking for more ground beef recipes.  The 25 most important recipes over the past 100 years.  Van Gough inspired Starry Night inspired this land!  How to fake storebought desserts for the holidays.  How to piecemeal Thanksgiving out of fast food.  How to doctor up boxed mashed potatoes.  Suncatcher stickers: one / two / three / four  I like the tile in this kitchen.  Need some mocktails for the holidays? Here are a few!  Need help navigating the holiday season & New Year? We’ve planned a workshop for you! Join MC & I for a live Zoom workshop where we will work together to build your holiday (survival) toolkit so you can reclaim holiday JOY again!  December 14th 10-12PM PST More info/sign-up here! I have another batch of Currently Workbooks in the shop now!  My Intentions for the Week Planner can help you get organized next year. It’s what we use to plan our week in my Self-Check-In group on The Hope Circuit.  Help me help you! Here are some deals!  Here’s 40% off your first Thrive Market order.  – I saved $450 last year!  Want extra discounts and cashback on online purchases? I use Rakuten religiously!  The holidays are coming up! Here are some of my favorite things from my Amazon storefront if you need gift ideas.  The post I LOVE LISTS appeared first on Shutterbean.
excerpt: Welcome to I LOVE LISTS. It's Friday and Tracy of Shutterbean.com shares her finds from the internet on a weekly list called I LOVE LISTS!
